OL,4,CCovid: Unpaid carers 'struggled to get
OL,5,Cpain relief' for terminally ill
OL,6, Unpaid carers looking after terminally
OL,7, ill friends and relatives during the
OL,8, pandemic struggled to access pain
OL,9, relief, with some patients dying in
OL,10, unnecessary pain, a survey has found.
OL,12,FThe survey of 995 unpaid carers by
OL,13,FMarie Curie also found people had
OL,14,Fdifficulties getting personal care and
OL,15,Frespite nursing for loved ones.
OL,17,FFigures show the number of people dying
OL,18,Fat home rose by 42% in the past year.
OL,20,FThe government said it had taken action
OL,21,Fto support unpaid carers.
